# Definition of Done

See `ai-framework/core/quality-gates.md`.

Do not mark a task complete unless:

- REQ acceptance criteria satisfied
- REQ has Type, MoSCoW, Priority
- Required tests pass
- Documentation updated for public API changes
- Validation gate satisfied when enabled
- Bugs recorded in required format
- Final report in PROJECT_LANGUAGE

Produce a final report explaining what changed and why.
